it.polimi.se2019.server.model

Class Tile

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.server.model.Tile
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Targetable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LootTile, SpawnTile

    public class Tile
extends Object
implements Targetable
    This class implements the tiles of the game map. Each tile is defined by its colour and has a list of grabbables which can both be weapons or a loot card. Each tiles has a map that defines its doors, the value of the map is true only when the tile has a door in the specified direction.
